guide: §7For this you will need Combat 15.
§7To blow up crypts you can use
§7class abilities (Tank, Archer, Mage)
§7and/or Superboom TNTs that drop
§7from slaying Minibosses in dungeons
§7and can be bought from Walther in
§7The Deep Caverns or Ophelia in
§7The Dungeon Hub.
§7You can buy this for a total of 400 coins
§7from the Fishing Merchant in the Hub.
§7For this you'll want to open structure chests
§7in the Crystal Hollows, do a Nucleus Run
§7(you will need a Small Gemstone Sack for this to count)
§7or kill Worms/Scathas.
§7Talk to the Blacksmith in the Hub
§7and gamble Reforges on an armor piece
§7until you get the Titanic Reforge.
§7You might need to bring some money for this.
§7Kill farm animals in the Barn with a Cleaver
§7with Cleave 5 and Sharpness 5
§7or spiders in Arachne's Burrow
§7in the Spider's Den with a Dreadlord Sword.
§7You can also kill Endermen in The End to
§7get progress towards the
§7Enderman Slayer Community Goal.
§7This unlocks at 5k Diamond Collection. Use Pure Ores
§7in the Dwarven Mines for this. Craft it with
§71 Enchanted Diamond and 8 Vines (costs 40 Jungle Leaves,
§7requires Jungle Wood Collection 4 to unlock it in /trades.)
§7Recommended for this is to fish in the
§7Backwater Bayou with the best rod you have
§7access to and full Angler Set or better.
§7You can also donate any special fish that you
§7get to Coral in Galatea (requires 1.21.5)
§7You'll unlock this recipe passively
§7(2.5k leather collection)
§7if you chose to do Exterminator in Barn.
§7Craft it with 592 Leather.
§7You can also use Cow Minions for this.
§7Do your daily Experimentation Tables
§7after getting Enchanting Level 10.
§7Mine Pure Emeralds in the Dwarven Mines
§7with a Fortune 3+ pickaxe.
§7You might want to use as many minions
§7as you have access to for this.
§7Remember to put a compactor in the minions
§7when you plan on leaving for a while.
§7Don't forget to fuel the minions,
§7give them storages and collect them in time.
§7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
§7by hand for Carpentry levels.
§7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
§7to have a pet active at all times
§7(any pet works, even level 100).
§7You will most likely get this passively.
§7Use /be ingame to view your progress once you
§7talked to Bramass Beastslayer in The Spiders Den.
§7Kill Team Treasurite members in the Crystal Hollows.
§7They spawn in the Mithril Deposits and you will need
§7Heart of the Mountain 4 to go there.
§7For this you may want to participate
§7in Mining Events in the Dwarven Mines
§7as you have a 20% chance to obtain
§7an Ultimate Enchanted Book from this.
§7You can also open Dungeon Reward Chests
§7for this. For that way you may require coins.
§7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor.
§7Recommended for this are:
§7Bingo, Rock and Grandma Wolf.
§7Talk to Guildford in the Dungeon Hub
§7and complete 4/4 objectives for 3 races.
§7Don't forget to talk to Guildford
§7after each run you do.
§7Start an Entrance floor and play Mage/Tank/Berserker to use
§7the classes abilities to kill a Lost Adventurer.
§7You only need to get the last hit
§7on it to count, so you can get help from your team.
§7You need Combat Level 15 to join a Dungeon.
§7Apply/Use the highest tier of Scavenger
§7that you can get your hands on and put it
§7on your main weapon. Gifts from the Jerry Island
§7can be a way to obtain Scavenger IV books.
§7You can also use the weapon drops from dungeon mobs
§7as those have guaranteed Scavenger 5.
§7For this you can farm some crops
§7in the Hub or do a bit of farming
§7in The Garden (needs SB Level 12).
§7Craft some easy minions while also getting
§7those that will help with this Bingo.
§7(meaning Cow, Gold, Emerald and maybe
§7Fishing Minion if you want to go for
§7Community Goals later)
§7Mine Pure Gold in the Dwarven Mines
§7or Gold Blocks in the Mines of Divan
§7(found in the Crystal Hollows,
§7needs HOTM 4 to enter)
§7with a Fortune 3+ pickaxe.
§7You might want to use as many minions
§7as you have access to for this.
§7Remember to put a compactor in the minions
§7when you plan on leaving for a while.
§7Don't forget to fuel the minions,
§7give them storages and collect them in time.
§7You can find Relic Coordinates in Skytils or the Wiki.
§7You will need Ender Pearls to reach some of them.
§7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
§7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
§7on xMeru's, skyerzz's or prtl's island.
§7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
§7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
§7Kill Endermen in The End using full Ender Armor
§7and a Void Sword or Dreadlord Sword.
